General.Name: Seacera Group Bhd
General.Description: Seacera Group Berhad engages in the trading of building materials in Malaysia. The company operates through Trading, and Property Development and Construction segments. It engages in the trading of tiles products, personal protective equipment products, and food and beverages. The company is also involved in the property development; and general construction and trading activities. In addition, it exports its products. The company was formerly known as Seacera Tiles Berhad and changed its name to Seacera Group Berhad in July 2011. Seacera Group Berhad was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Batu Caves, Malaysia.
